 rel="noopener noreferrer" data-web-url="http://www.bloombergview.com/topics/masters-in-business">商业硕士学位</a>，他创立并领导了哈佛法学院的行为经济学和公共政策项目。他撰写了多本书，包括畅销书《 <a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0300122233/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>助推：改善有关健康、财富和幸福的决策</em></a>》。 （与诺贝尔奖获得者理查德·塞勒合着）和《纽约时报》畅销书《 <a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0062484222/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星球大战中的世界</a>》。他的新书是《 <a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1009400460/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">关于决策的决策：日常生活中的实践理性</a>》。</p><p></p><p> <strong>91% 的美国抵押贷款借款人的抵押贷款利率低于 5.01%</strong><br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/below5.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-318669" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/below5.jpeg" alt="" width="650" height="470" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/below5.jpeg 733w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/below5-300x217.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/below5-250x181.jpeg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" /></a><br />资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/NewsLambert/status/1693650460895273186" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@NewsLambert</a></p><p></p><p> <a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://mailchi.mp/005fb77d75b9/ritholtzreads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>在此注册我们的只读邮件列表</em></a>。</p><p></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/08/10-wednesday-am-reads-344/">周三上午 10 点阅读的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">The Big Picture</a>上。</p> ;
